UPDATE products SET blurb = 'Our Mullein Leaf now comes in 4 oz., 8 oz., and bulk sizes. Verbascum thapsus is a fuzzy-leaved, herbaceous biennial in the Scrophulariaceae family.', description = 'Our Mullein Leaf now comes in 4 oz., 8 oz., and bulk sizes.

