UPDATE products SET blurb = 'Ulva lactuca is an edible green seaweed found in shallow, rocky, coastal shorelines around the world. The aqueous plant has thin, almost sheet-like, lobed and ruffled edges resembling a head of green leaf lettuce.', description = 'Ulva lactuca is an edible green seaweed found in shallow, rocky, coastal shorelines around the world. The aqueous plant has thin, almost sheet-like, lobed and ruffled edges resembling a head of green leaf lettuce. Sea lettuce is typically added to culinary dishes for its nutritious value. Popular in Scotland, sea lettuce flakes are often added to soups and salads.

