UPDATE products SET blurb = 'Pausinystalia johimbe is a stately evergreen tree growing up to 100 feet in height. Native to western and central Africa, yohimbe grows in lowland forests.', description = 'Pausinystalia johimbe is a stately evergreen tree growing up to 100 feet in height. Native to western and central Africa, yohimbe grows in lowland forests. The tree has grey to reddish-brown bark and oval-shaped leaves which are grouped into threes. Yohimbe, also referred to johimbi, belongs to the Rubiaceae plant family.

